都冇發生過咁復原出返黎<br />\n<br />\n另邊廂, 4代目個呢個後輩不自量力硬食黑波, 冇完1條手臂跟住再冇1條<br />\n結果以人棍狀態到完場收工, 非常不堪入目"},{"pid":"d7e91c873dadf16b57e626ebc658dfa5fb3b1dec","tid":833821,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a2510d308732b585fc89284492c7dcf1c8d918d","tid":833821,"uid":34377,"like":74,"dislike":18,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"d728d0671b50e0728826f3f1e5f94fe27d473a77","tid":833821,"uid":140523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T18:52:18.000Z","msg":"自來也識仙術<br />\n大蛇丸又識白蛇仙人<br />\n綱手識括瑜既通靈術<br />\n三忍同三大祕境都有關係<br />\n輸比大蛇丸只係老 通靈唔到勁野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:14:57.000Z","msg":"自來也 都唔算後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔同 班外掛比，佢已經係最勁果批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既年齡，仲要一打三，其中兩個係全盛期姿態復活既初代，二代兩兄弟<br />\n<br />\n一個屍鬼封盡 封左初代，二代兩兄弟 再封大蛇丸雙手 唔俾佢再忍術<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T19:17:30.000Z","msg":"去到忍界大戰復活初代完全兩個水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f49bb266cddfc4837b64b385da11a60ec2025c8","tid":833821,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b355eb4d4c973680d2d2adf999cc87b0d1b36df3","tid":833821,"uid":28823,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"225a38caf59ad142380f0a9aef22b61471af4cd1","tid":833821,"uid":34929,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"505e279527a656198ae7398036ce73739f7c3e9a","tid":833821,"uid":28823,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"睇親依兩個比較都笑撚到停唔到..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/7LPD58.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2F7LPD58.gif&h=0694d24d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"笑撚到停唔到，打仙人仲用手裹劍..痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T19:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256433cdc87489600a7da206d7c087858d7c4f0e","tid":833821,"uid":122471,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"第2次九尾襲村(帶土發起果次), <br />\n成場戰役入面, 歷代最強火影之神3代目動作唔多<br />\n亦唔使多,佢淨係出左1招(叫猿魔變棒棒再伸長)<br />\n其餘99%時間行行企企、散步, +睇9尾球壞, +睇傻仔4代同偽斑隻揪<br />\n+睇4代同9尾隻揪, +睇4代同老婆&amp;9尾攬炒, 完美監察全程發展並掌握局勢<br />\n4代死埋, 3代目出力全村最少功勞全村最大, 薑係老既辣真係冇講錯<br />\n<br />\n又識抄4代家沒收佢家產, 故意唔俾個官2代啊鳴人似寵生嬌<br />\n俾佢由細細個開始就同9尾1齊建立關係、培養感情, 並傳承火之意志<br />\n<br />\n又識俾團藏搞旺木葉, 將組識根發大黎搞, 冧自己友劈埋對手邊個擋路劏邊個<br />\n又識善用鼬既才幹屠自己全族, 但又故意留佐助活口俾佢係村1齊生活感受家庭溫暖<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係有3代? 木葉1早玩完啦!"},{"pid":"81903bf0c1245733042f24e7b35f17c05202183f","tid":833821,"uid":62133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f114461f7ed951992097d0a69f6c806909ccc1e","tid":833821,"uid":87749,"like":75,"dislike":3,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"7a2510d308732b585fc89284492c7dcf1c8d918d","tid":833821,"uid":34377,"like":74,"dislike":18,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"d728d0671b50e0728826f3f1e5f94fe27d473a77","tid":833821,"uid":140523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T18:52:18.000Z","msg":"自來也識仙術<br />\n大蛇丸又識白蛇仙人<br />\n綱手識括瑜既通靈術<br />\n三忍同三大祕境都有關係<br />\n輸比大蛇丸只係老 通靈唔到勁野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:14:57.000Z","msg":"自來也 都唔算後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔同 班外掛比，佢已經係最勁果批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既年齡，仲要一打三，其中兩個係全盛期姿態復活既初代，二代兩兄弟<br />\n<br />\n一個屍鬼封盡 封左初代，二代兩兄弟 再封大蛇丸雙手 唔俾佢再忍術<br />\n<br 